name: Tezos Will Climb - Teztune
description:
I just wanna see that you can hold. 
These devs don’t wanna hear you bitch and moan.
Do you want decentralized or sacrifice for higher highs?
When the avalanche falls Tezos will climb.  
If you’re focused on the chart to BTC. 
You’re probably in telegram fudding. 
Yes we have all heard this sob story. 
If you can’t see what we’re building, 
take your loss and leave.   
You keep dumping I’ll keep pumping. 
Perfect for accumulating. 
Every day is just more time,
 To prepare for the true king to shine.  
Paper hands need not apply.
 This is not the chain that pumps on hype. 
But we’ve got the best NFTs,  DeFi capabilities, 
We just keep on upgrading our technology.
